      • makeJsonSongRequest

        private void makeJsonSongRequest()
        Makes JSONObjectRequest to SERVER/search?q=[TEXT], where TEXT is a string to what the user is searching. Adds request to VolleySingleton request queue. Server responds with a json string containing a list of albums, osngs, and artist from Spotify.

      • makeStringSongRequest

        private void makeStringSongRequest()
        Makes StringRequest to SERVER/search?q=[TEXT], where TEXT is a string to what the user is searching. Adds request to VolleySingleton request queue. Server responds with a string containing a list of albums, osngs, and artist from Spotify.
